de.unibox.client.thread.worker

Class RunnableCometListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unibox.client.thread.implementation.ThreadTaskImpl
      • de.unibox.client.thread.worker.RunnableCometListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class RunnableCometListener
extends ThreadTaskImpl
    The listener interface for receiving runnableComet events. The class that is interested in processing a runnableComet event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addRunnableCometListener method. When the runnableComet event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked. Incoming Messages will be handled here.
